* {{a|UK}} {{IPA|/əʊˈtɑːkuː/|[əʊ̯ˈtʰɑːkuː]|lang=en}}
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|/oʊˈtɑku/|[oʊ̯ˈtʰɑku]|lang=en}}
* {{audio|en-us-otaku.ogg|Audio (US)|lang=en}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{label|en|fandom}} One with an [[obsessive]] interest in something, particularly [[anime]] or [[manga]].

